extends ../layout

block content
    .red
        h1.red Manage Seasons
        p.page_width You can use this page to add seasons to the league. You can use the order numbers to move seasons around in dropdowns.
        form(action='/admin/seasons',method='POST')
            input(type='hidden',name='post_type',value='edit')
            table.page_width.colorized
                tr
                    th(colspan=3) Seasons Management
                tr
                    th ID
                    th Label
                    th Order
                if seasons.length > 0
                    for season in seasons
                        tr
                            td.center=season.season_id
                            td.center.half_page_width
                                input(type='hidden',name='season_id',value=season.season_id)
                                input(type='text',name='label',value=season.label)
                            td.center
                                input(type='text',name='order',value=season.order,size=5)
                    tr
                        th(colspan=3)
                            button(type='submit') Update Seasons
                else
                    tr
                        td.center(colspan=3) No Seasons.
        br
        p.page_width You can add a season using this menu below.
        h1.page_width NOTE: Adding a new season will force logout all users with outdated applications so they can signup for the new season.
        form(action='/admin/seasons',method='POST')
            input(type='hidden',name='post_type',value='add')
            table.page_width.colorized
                tr
                    th(colspan=2) Add Season
                tr
                    th.half_page_width Label
                    th Order
                tr
                    td.center
                        input(type='text',name='label',size=30)
                    td.center Goes to top
                tr
                    th(colspan=2)
                        button(type='submit') Add Season
